_sText: There are only 3 textures on this map. The checks, the whizzy one for my name and the skybox. The custom textures are zipped with the bsp so no need to download the textures. If you you want the textures then PM me. I made this map completely alone and its my second map on fpsbanana yet my 5th altogether. This map is better finished than my last (gg_circular_advanced) although i am going to tweek that one later on. Please download and rate me and the map. And lastly, have fun on the map and put it all your servers!
